<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TERMINAL SUARA | PARI AR-RANIRY</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        /* Desain Terminal Suara */
        .voice-terminal {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: #050505;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(74, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Label Status di Sudut */
        .voice-terminal::after {
            content: "SECURE TRANSMISSION ACTIVE";
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 20px;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: #4a0000;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            color: #d4af37;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }

        input[type="text"], 
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            background: #000;
            border: 1px solid #222;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 1rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            border-color: #ff0000;
            background: #080000;
        }

        .btn-transmit {
            background: #4a0000;
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #600;
            padding: 18px;
            width: 100%;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn-transmit:hover {
            background: #ff0000;
            border-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .warning-box {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px dashed #333;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .status-dot {
            height: 8px;
            width: 8px;
            background-color: #ff0000;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
            animation: blink 1s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #444;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .back-link:hover { color: #fff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← KEMBALI KE TERMINAL UTAMA</a>

        <main class="voice-terminal">
            <h1 style="font-style: italic; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 5px;">Dinding Subversi</h1>
            <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 40px;">Saluran komunikasi anonim untuk pelaporan birokrasi dan gagasan perlawanan.</p>

            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xaqvkjaa" method="POST">
                
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Kode Alias / Identitas Samaran</label>
                    <input type="text" name="alias" placeholder="Contoh: @HantuFakultas / Anon_Raniry" required>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Subjek Transmisi</label>
                    <input type="text" name="subject" placeholder="Contoh: Laporan Pungli / Gagasan Aksi" required>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label>Isi Manifes / Laporan</label>
                    <textarea name="message" rows="8" placeholder="Tuliskan keresahanmu secara detail di sini..." required></textarea>
                </div>

                <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Transmisi Baru dari Dinding Subversi PARI">

                <button type="submit" class="btn-transmit">Kirim Transmisi</button>

            </form>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <p><span class="status-dot"></span> <strong>CATATAN KEAMANAN:</strong></p>
                <p>Setiap transmisi yang dikirim melalui jalur ini dienkripsi melalui protokol Formspree. PARI tidak mengumpulkan metadata perangkat. Keamanan identitas Anda adalah prioritas mutlak kami. Data yang masuk akan dikurasi secara manual sebelum diarsipkan ke dalam log utama.</p>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
